{"tid":639403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港女戀上「非洲難民」：「我不介意養他」","createTime":"2018-04-23T12:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T13:43:39.000Z","uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88f79905c50b4cc1aa7a98aeea5e104c3b329b0d","tid":639403,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/203057_650350c74515de439bb4547796ee2d92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F203057_650350c74515de439bb4547796ee2d92.jpg&h=c0adf48d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港女生阿凝（Louise Chan，中文名為化名）在一支難民足球隊中，結識了未婚夫索羅曼（Solomon Nyassi）。<br />\n<br />\n兩人接受BBC中文採訪時，分享了他們在香港如何備受歧視，和應對「假結婚」的指控。<br />\n<br />\n文字版：香港女生戀上「非洲難民」之後<br />\n來自岡比亞的索羅曼因為政治理由來香港尋求庇護，但香港政府不承認任何「難民」，也不會提供庇護，索羅曼等尋求庇護者不能夠工作，每月只靠約3000港元生活。<br />\n<br />\n但兩人下月結婚，意味可以透過申請伴侶簽證，讓索羅曼在香港工作。<br />\n<br />\n阿凝稱兩人是真心相愛，結婚是經過詳細考慮，不認為索羅曼會欺騙她，現在也不介意每個月向索羅曼提供生活費。而索羅曼亦表示，這是一段認真的關係，自己希望可以在香港工作，養活家人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-43861501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-43861501&d=Z6pmzW275clul0h%2FI4j3NjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=10c6747c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-43861501&h=25ef9a90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-43861501</a>"},{"pid":"525f5872a4bf91bb55a48e411c966dd711b958ab","tid":639403,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"你一個養一隊波都得啦"},{"pid":"0ae5549f61a45e0e2107c2d2ec40009d1443fcf3","tid":639403,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"睇得出多水夠大食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed53054dc360ec64e4e2ffc1be05549ca618238","tid":639403,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"黑色巨根x肥婆"}]}